      • threeWayRecommend

        public abstract int[][] threeWayRecommend(int paraUser)
        One round three-way recommend. Both currentUserRecommendations and currentUserPromotions should be updated here.
        参数:
        paraUser - The user.
        返回:
        Recommendations/promotions of the current round. It is an integer matrix, where the first row indicates recommended items, while the second indicates promoted ones.
